Regional Sales Beverage Head
Responsibilities
Key responsibilities :Prepare sales target and action planManage sales team in term of people management and also daily sales operationEnsure the coverage of beverage product in term of availability and visibility in modern trade and traditional/general tradeCollaborate with Trade Marketing to implement trade marketing program effectivelyBuild relationship with customer (especially wholesaler)Manage partner and sub distributor and support them to achieve beverage sales targetMonitor competitor activities and anticipate any possibilities that can impact the market shareKey requirements :Bachelor degree in any disciplineMinimum eight years experience in FMCG handling beverage productStrong leadership and creativeGood communication and interpersonal skillsFluent in English both oral and writing
Requirements
Company Overview
Robert Walters Jakarta was established in 2012 and due to continual expansion is seeking highly entrepreneurial, motivated recruitment consultants to grow the business. Jakarta is one of the worlds largest cities, is internationalising rapidly, with a corresponding increase in demand for an international standard of recruitment services. Robert Walters is one of the world's leading global specialist recruitment and recruitment outsourcing businesses. The Group specialises in permanent and contract recruitment across all industry sectors, and count FORTUNE 500 companies, investment banks and multinational blue-chip commercial organisations as clients. Operating at all levels of seniority, Jakarta - Indonesia office manages the careers of the best professionals in the following disciplines: commerce finance, banking & financial services, engineering, human resources, legal, information technology, sales & marketing, supply chain, procurement & logistics, and support and administration fields. A leading multinational beverage company is looking for Regional Sales Beverage Head to be based in Jakarta.  Reporting to the General Manager Sales, you will be responsible for sales revenue in Jakarta region.
